baseline_groups.claim_summary: Same-denomination church competition within 4 miles is positively associated with the probability of providing childcare.
baseline_groups.notes: Logit of binary childcare provision on same-denomination church count within 4 miles, full controls, county FE. Coef=0.067 (p=0.170). Original paper uses structural GMM; this is a reduced-form approximation.

baseline_groups.claim_summary: Different-denomination church competition within 4 miles is positively associated with the probability of providing childcare.
baseline_groups.notes: Secondary baseline from the same regression as G1, reporting coefficient on different-denomination competition. Coef=0.025 (p=0.375). No robustness specs directly target this coefficient.

global_notes: 60 reduced-form specifications from a paper that originally used structural GMM. Two baselines from the same regression (different treatment variables). Most robustness specs target same_denom_4mi (G1). Several city-level subsamples suffer from separation issues. Heterogeneity specs report interaction coefficients not main effects.
